    "translations": {
      "en": {
        "summary": "This hadith provides another chain of transmission for the interpretation of Quran 37:130, where Ibn Abbas identifies \"the Family of Yasin\" as the family of Prophet Muhammad (s). This narration through al-Kalbi and Abu Salih represents one of the most widely cited tafsir chains for this verse, emphasizing that the divine greeting of peace is directed at the Prophet's household (Ahl al-Bayt).",
        "key_terms": {
          "إل ياسين": "The Family of Yasin - interpreted as the Family of Muhammad",
          "آل محمد": "The Family of Muhammad - referring to Ahl al-Bayt"
        },
        "seo_question": "What did Ibn Abbas say about \"Peace be upon the Family of Yasin\" in Quran 37:130?"
      },
      "ur": {
        "summary": "یہ حدیث آیت 37:130 کی تفسیر کا ایک اور سلسلہ سند فراہم کرتی ہے جہاں ابن عباس نے \"آل یاسین\" کو آل محمد (ص) قرار دیا ہے۔ یہ اہل بیت کی فضیلت پر زور دیتی ہے۔",
        "key_terms": {
          "إل ياسين": "آل یاسین - آل محمد کی تعبیر",
          "آل محمد": "آل محمد - اہل بیت کی طرف اشارہ"
